nginx module to generate secure download links that can be used in combination with the module ngx_http_secure_download. 

ngx_http_generate_secure_download_links should be used via ssi, so it can replace ssi tags by secured download links on the fly

there is a howto by example: http://mauro-stettler.blogspot.com/2010/07/generate-secured-download-links-on-fly.html
